class Solution {
    public int maxSubArray(int[] nums) {
        int max = Integer.MIN_VALUE;
        int sum = 0;
        for(int c : nums){
            sum += c;
             if (sum > max) max = sum;
            if (sum<0) sum = 0;
           
        }
        return max;
    }
}
//Two variable concept , max ko min integer rakhna h and jab bhi sum < 0 ho toh possible outcome ke wajah se uss subarray ko discard karna h ,
Example 1:
Input: nums = [-2,1,-3,4,-1,2,1,-5,4]
Output: 6
Explanation: The subarray [4,-1,2,1] has the largest sum 6
untill 4 , sum negative hi hai thats why skip karenge iteration .
